descriptionHtml:
Edit: woops I forgot to upload the file when I created the page :p But it\'s available to download now! Sorry guys!


This mod adds secret passages to enter the fortified main cities of Skyrim.

Here is a video link to see where are the entrances: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ysKKfYKe5PI

If you have any suggestions, please feel free to comment :)

Hope to help you thieves brothers, may the shadows be with you!
